gw.api.graph

Class EntityGraphTraverser

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.graph.traverse.GraphTraverserBase<KeyableBean>
      • gw.api.graph.EntityGraphTraverser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphTraverser<KeyableBean>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContactSubgraphTraverser

    public class EntityGraphTraverser
extends GraphTraverserBase<KeyableBean>
    A implementation of GraphTraverser for a graph of entity instances that traverses the graph using outgoing edges from each node that is visited. Note that this implementation will not visit any nodes that are not reachable from links going outward from the root entity.
    Author:
    bspies
